  "impact_on_program": {
    "H": "|H|\u2264(n/e)L; need L\u226470 for |H|\u22642170, or use tier thinning",
    "SR": "\u03bc_enum gives constructive e\u00b7p SR injection whenever N_S\u2264e\u00b7p (ensured by |H|\u22642170). Local drop of c0U from \u03bc\u2082 still fails.",
